        {
            "title": "兩新股登場齊高收 滬上阿姨漲40% 鈞達亦升20%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今日登場兩新股均成功令認購投資者獲利，其中滬上阿姨(02589)表現領先，收報158.4元，較招股價高40.03%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"滬上阿姨圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/02/20250118_BLOG_AUNTEA-JENNY_03.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"滬上阿姨圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/02/20250118_BLOG_AUNTEA-JENNY_03.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">滬上阿姨圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股全日均高於招股價113.12元，最低價152元，也高於招股價34.37%；最高曾見197.6元，比招股價高74.68%。以收市價158.4元及每手30股計，認購並獲配1手賬面賺1358.4元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"鈞達新能源官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"鈞達新能源官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">鈞達新能源官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另一隻新股鈞達(02865)表現也勝預期，雖然曾失守招股價22.15元，但最低只見22.1元；最高則報27.5元，較招股價高24.15%。該股收報26.6元，高於招股價20.09%；以1手100股計，認購及獲配每手賬面也賺445元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913046-%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e9%bd%8a%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b6-%e6%bb%ac%e4%b8%8a%e9%98%bf%e5%a7%a8%e6%bc%b240-%e9%88%9e%e9%81%94%e4%ba%a6%e5%8d%8720",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_02589.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 16:36:05",
