            "title": "港股午後升幅收窄至百點以下  康師傅挫逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數午後升幅收窄百點以下，現升92點或0.41%，報22784  ; 恒生國企指數報8298點，升56點或0.68%  ; 恒生科技指數升29點或0.57%，報5229點。     </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交1502.13億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"康師傅官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/00322.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"康師傅官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/00322.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">康師傅官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015)升5.35%，報106.3元 ; 吉利(00175)升3.81%，報17.42元 ; 藥明生物(02269)升3.46%，報22.45元。三股藍籌股中表現最佳。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">康師傅(00322)跌3.31%，報13.46元 ; 百度(09888)跌3.03%，報84.75元 ; 中芯(00981)報2.81%，報44.9元，三股藍籌股中表現最差。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)跌2.82%，報179.3元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">衛龍美味(09985)趺5.26%，報15.14元。</p>\n</div>",
